Cell["\<\
Calculating the midpoint in Wolfram Language using the built-in Midpoint \
function:\
\>", "CodeText",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992441366101939*^9, 
  3.992441380836669*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"dd495d36-fd48-4932-a3e2-\
