    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{"p3", ",", "p5"}], "}"}], "]"}]}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9920971010732193`*^9, 3.992097111077364*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[26]:=",ExpressionUUID->"b63ac47c-d652-41fa-a50d-afd9fa82600c"],

Cell["\<\
With all of the points now defined, I began calculating for the torque. The \
equation for torque is known as:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992097266395308*^9, 3.9920972777812233`*^9}, {
   3.9920974531310387`*^9, 3.992097472807303*^9}, {3.992097745948107*^9, 
   3.9920981476796417`*^9}, {3.992421033765835*^9, 3.992421033879548*^9}, {
   3.992441390140338*^9, 3.9924413916989183`*^9}, {3.9925974258569527`*^9, 
   3.99259747202188*^9}, {3.992598757839549*^9, 3.99259875926333*^9}, 
   3.992601531064232*^9},ExpressionUUID->"430b3f92-a0fe-4e65-a581-\
6af88826dc0d"],

Cell["\[Tau] = F*r*sin(\[Theta])", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992097266395308*^9, 3.9920972777812233`*^9}, {
   3.9920974531310387`*^9, 3.992097472807303*^9}, {3.992097745948107*^9, 
   3.9920981476796417`*^9}, {3.992421033765835*^9, 3.992421033879548*^9}, {
   3.992441390140338*^9, 3.9924413916989183`*^9}, {3.9925974258569527`*^9, 
   3.99259747202188*^9}, {3.992598757839549*^9, 3.99259875926333*^9}, 
   3.9926015323784027`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"8d021976-acd6-b443-bf59-\
79ba96bbeead"],

Cell["\<\
Assuming the force to be gravitational force, then F = m * g.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992097266395308*^9, 3.9920972777812233`*^9}, {
   3.9920974531310387`*^9, 3.992097472807303*^9}, {3.992097745948107*^9, 
   3.9920981476796417`*^9}, {3.992421033765835*^9, 3.992421033879548*^9}, {
   3.992441390140338*^9, 3.9924413916989183`*^9}, {3.9925974258569527`*^9, 
   3.99259747202188*^9}, {3.992598757839549*^9, 3.99259875926333*^9}, 
   3.9926015395333157`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"8ffcd50c-f0b3-7a4d-bc1d-\
9022a57b5fad"],

Cell["\<\
I then defined the torque exerted on the coordinate plane through generic \
placeholders. In this case, there is a point mass at (x,y) with mass m, \
distance r, and angle \[Theta] from the origin (0,0).\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992097266395308*^9, 3.9920972777812233`*^9}, {
  3.9920974531310387`*^9, 3.992097472807303*^9}, {3.992097745948107*^9, 
