Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Model V2 - Self-Balancing Tail with Variable Rotation", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992549151613921*^9, 
  3.9925491578203*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d2796933-5317-47b1-9a87-201ef3b6c594"],

Cell["\<\
The model V1 works, however it is inaccurate to any animal\[CloseCurlyQuote]s \
behavior in nature. An animal cannot grow or shrink its tail in real-time. \
The V1 also assumes that the monkey\[CloseCurlyQuote]s tail is always \
perpendicular to its body. In nature, this is also not the case.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9921006037133503`*^9, 3.992100622324725*^9}, {
   3.992112560594152*^9, 3.992112565902768*^9}, {3.992112666101972*^9, 
   3.992112771642489*^9}, {3.9921128088760357`*^9, 3.992112976802414*^9}, {
   3.992113080218974*^9, 3.9921131016507053`*^9}, {3.9921131343634853`*^9, 
   3.992113141870468*^9}, 3.992114640303331*^9, {3.9924417871062593`*^9, 
   3.992441787471518*^9}, {3.992597555211034*^9, 3.9925975789356203`*^9}, 
   3.992601576811844*^9, {3.9926024901519623`*^9, 
   3.992602491499401*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"570c5638-2d52-4e0e-ac5b-\
5129396db615"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Instead, to counterbalance its mass, a monkey will change the angle of its \
tail. To achieve this, I adjusted the math behind the model, giving ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["d", "tail"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1551bbf7-332a-f941-887b-e00c0a260a23"],
 " a value, and defining a new constant for the angle of the tail, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "adj"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "5892119b-2228-2d4d-8f2c-0b9ab35667f7"],
 "."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9921006037133503`*^9, 3.992100622324725*^9}, {
   3.992112560594152*^9, 3.992112565902768*^9}, {3.992112666101972*^9, 
   3.992112771642489*^9}, {3.9921128088760357`*^9, 3.992112976802414*^9}, {
   3.992113080218974*^9, 3.9921131016507053`*^9}, {3.9921131343634853`*^9, 
   3.992113141870468*^9}, 3.992114640303331*^9, {3.9924417871062593`*^9, 
   3.992441787471518*^9}, {3.992597555211034*^9, 3.9925975789356203`*^9}, {
   3.9926025187973595`*^9, 
   3.992602528106983*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d2dd50ea-b3cc-b74d-b7c8-\
25c79f2abcc7"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Redefining the constants and coordinates ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "6"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "ecb89e22-0748-45ef-b63a-f5226d68363c"],
 " , ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1561f2df-6fc4-4b6c-abe7-e10caa50dca9"],
 ", ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "3"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "133fe11c-bab6-4043-a42d-b9e39f5877be"],
 ", and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["p", "1"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "31476628-3804-4999-9676-2f07787f2dad"],
 " as they do not change from the V1."
}], "CodeText",
