}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9926016274488163`*^9, 
  3.992601634332739*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"02e36221-580b-f24d-8241-\
f8a747656fef"],

Cell["\<\
The diagram below shows an example of all of these rules, in this case with 3 \
segments for the tail:\
