 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "3"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8a899e42-732e-864f-abdc-8ffa56e7ac39"],
 ", they use the current ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "adj"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e34ce273-75ac-6143-b30c-768b0ee6d134"],
 " with the past ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["\[Theta]", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "2425abdc-d1b4-544c-86d8-59fece042b30"],
 ". This means I could develop and implement the following formula:"
}], "Text",
