   3.9926033226463814`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"2d244990-5d47-d14e-ac72-\
2d6ae42a7755"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Just like the previous NSolve functions in Wolfram for the previous two \
models, I computed each of the ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Theta]", "adj"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "7acf62df-650a-4647-b330-e11ca6e4a779"],
 " values. Before computing the values, I defined constraints such that all \
of the joints do not fold on each other."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.992430546160564*^9, 3.992430574793579*^9}, {
  3.992430647446924*^9, 3.992430686038555*^9}, {3.9924307408162403`*^9, 
