Cell["\<\
I would like to extend my sincerest gratitude towards the staff at Wolfram \
Research for granting me this incredible opportunity, notably program \
directors Rory Foulger, Eryn Gillam, and Megan Davis. A special mention as \
well goes towards founder and CEO of Wolfram Research, Dr. Stephen Wolfram, \
for his development of my project idea and management of the research. Thank \
you to my mentor Mr. Angel Rojas, who contributed to my foundations in \
Wolfram Language, refactoring of my code, revision of my writing, and \
brainstorming for my math. I also extend my thankfulness towards the Teaching \
Assistants (TAs) of the 2026 Wolfram High School Summer Research Program, \
notably Arnay Garyhan who helped with my final model, Aanya Gupta, who aided \
in editing my essay for flow and formatting, and Eric Archerman, who helped \
with a large portion of the math derivations. Finally, I would like to \
recognize my family, notably parents for their motivation and guidance and \
recommending me to apply to this program, my grandfather for his thoughtful \
advice, and my sister for her endless support.\
\>", "Text",
